==English==

===Etymology===
1814, from {{compound|hand|book|lang=en}}, or perhaps a reintroduction of {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|handbōc}} "handbook", or a loan-translation of {{cog|de|Handbuch}}
"handbook". Compare {{cog|nl|handboek}}, {{cog|da|håndbog}}, {{cog|sv|handbok}}.

